summary: An ordinance amending Section 15 of Ordinance No. 15855 entitled: "An ordinance to license and regulate certain trades and occupations in the City of Seattle, and providing penalties for violation thereof" approved April 25, 1907, as amended by Ordinance No. 26270, approved February 4, 1911, for the purpose of placing the granting of employment agency licenses under the control of the City Council.
